#. Tag: title
#: details-categories.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid "Categories"
msgstr "Kategorije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Internally, Categories are treated by &kmymoney; as a special type of "
"account, so many of the features of Categories are very similar to those of "
"other Accounts."
msgstr ""
"Interno &kmymoney; obravnava kategorije kot posebna vrsta računa, zato je "
"veliko funkcij kategorij zelo podobnih funkcijam drugih računov."

#. Tag: title
#: details-categories.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Categories View"
msgstr "Pogled kategorij"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-categories.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>categories view</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pogled kategorij</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-categories.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>categories view</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pogled kategorij</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Categories View provides a summary of all the existing categories in "
"your current data file. Similar to the Accounts View, categories are grouped "
"into Income and Expense. As with the Institutions View and Accounts View, "
"the list of categories can be expanded or collapsed by clicking the arrow to "
"the left of the type or name. As with Asset and Liability Accounts, "
"Categories can be considered subcategories, with a parent of another "
"category instead of the top-level Income or Expense."
msgstr ""
"Pogled kategorij ponuja povzetek vseh obstoječih kategorij v vaši trenutni "
"podatkovni datoteki. Podobno kot v pogledu računov so kategorije združene v "
"prihodke in stroške. Tako kot pri pogledu institucij in pogledu računov "
"lahko seznam kategorij razširite ali strnete s klikom na puščico na levi "
"strani vrste ali imena. Tako kot pri računih sredstev in obveznosti se lahko "
"kategorije obravnavajo kot podkategorije, pri čemer je nadrejena druga "
"kategorija namesto prihodkov ali odhodkov na najvišji ravni."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to the Accounts View, the Categories View displays several columns "
"with descriptive and summary information about each category. As with the "
"Accounts View, you can select which columns are shown by right-clicking any "
"column heading and selecting or unselecting the checkbox next to the name of "
"the column."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot pogled računov, pogled kategorij prikazuje več stolpcev z "
"opisnimi in povzetki informacij o vsaki kategoriji. Tako kot pri pogledu "
"računov lahko izberete, kateri stolpci bodo prikazani, tako da z desno "
"miškino tipko kliknete naslov stolpca in izberete ali počistite potrditveno "
"polje poleg imena stolpca."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The columns available for Categories are identical to those for Accounts for "
"Name, Type, Tax, VAT, Balance, and Total Value. Online, Account Number, and "
"IBAN are not applicable to Categories. There is one additional column "
"available."
msgstr ""
"Stolpci, ki so na voljo za kategorije, so enaki tistim za račune za ime, "
"vrsto, davek, DDV, stanje in skupno vrednost. Online, številka računa in "
"IBAN ne veljajo za kategorije. Na voljo je en dodaten stolpec."

#. Tag: term
#: details-categories.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>CC</term>"
msgstr "<term>CC</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An indication that a cost center assignment is necessary under certain "
"conditions when entering a transaction for this category. This is a recently "
"added feature, which is not yet implemented, so this column is not currently "
"used. In addition, it may not show up at all, depending on the value of a "
"build time configuration setting."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka, da je pri vnosu transakcije za to kategorijo pod določenimi pogoji "
"potrebna dodelitev stroškovnega mesta. To je nedavno dodana funkcija, ki še "
"ni implementirana, zato se ta stolpec trenutno ne uporablja. Poleg tega se "
"morda sploh ne prikaže, odvisno od vrednosti konfiguracijske nastavitve časa "
"gradnje."

#. Tag: title
#: details-categories.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a category"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje kategorije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are 3 ways to create a new category: select the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Category</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New category</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menu item, right-click a parent in the tree in the Categories "
"View and select the <guimenuitem>New Category</guimenuitem> option, or "
"directly type the name of the new category when adding or editing a "
"transaction in the Ledger. Doing any of these steps will direct you to the "
"<guilabel>Create a new Category</guilabel> dialog. This dialog contains "
"three tabs: <guilabel>General</guilabel>, <guilabel>Hierarchy</guilabel>, "
"and <guilabel>Tax</guilabel>. The General tab includes editable fields for "
"the new category name, type, and currency (with the default currency "
"preselected,) as well as options for Last check number, Notes, and a "
"checkbox for Cost Center assignment required. In the Hierarchy tab, you are "
"able to select the appropriate parent for the category. Finally, in the Tax "
"tab, there are fields to enable and configure VAT support, and a checkbox to "
"include this category in tax related reports."
msgstr ""
"Novo kategorijo lahko ustvarite na 3 načine: izberite menijski element "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Kategorija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova kategorija</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, z desno miškino tipko kliknite nadrejenega v "
"drevesu v Kategorijah Oglejte si in izberite možnost <guimenuitem>Nova "
"kategorija</guimenuitem> ali neposredno vnesite ime nove kategorije, ko "
"dodajate ali urejate transakcijo v Ledgerju. Izvedba katerega koli od teh "
"korakov vas bo usmerila v pogovorno okno <guilabel>Ustvari novo kategorijo</"
"guilabel>. To pogovorno okno vsebuje tri zavihke: <guilabel>Splošno</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Hierarhija</guilabel> in <guilabel>Davek</guilabel>. "
"Zavihek Splošno vključuje polja, ki jih je mogoče urejati, za novo ime "
"kategorije, vrsto in valuto (z vnaprej izbrano privzeto valuto), kot tudi "
"možnosti za zadnjo kontrolno številko, opombe in potrditveno polje za "
"zahtevano dodelitev stroškovnega mesta. V zavihku Hierarhija lahko izberete "
"ustreznega nadrejenega elementa za kategorijo. Končno so na zavihku Davki "
"polja za omogočanje in konfiguriranje podpore za DDV ter potrditveno polje "
"za vključitev te kategorije v poročila, povezana z davki."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-categories.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>create new category</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>ustvari novo kategorijo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-categories.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>create new category</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>ustvari novo kategorijo</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-categories.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing a Category"
msgstr "Urejanje kategorije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To edit a category, right-click a category name in the Category View, and "
"choose <guimenuitem>Edit category...</guimenuitem>. A window appears with "
"the same three tabs as the <guilabel>Create a new Category</guilabel> "
"dialog: General, Hierarchy, and Tax. Each tab allows you to edit certain "
"details of the category."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti kategorijo, z desno tipko miške kliknite ime kategorije v "
"pogledu kategorije in izberite <guimenuitem>Uredi kategorijo ...</"
"guimenuitem>. Prikaže se okno z enakimi tremi zavihki kot pogovorno okno "
"<guilabel>Ustvari novo kategorijo</guilabel>: Splošno, Hierarhija in Davek. "
"Vsak zavihek omogoča urejanje določenih podrobnosti kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The General tab allows you to edit the name of the category, any notes you "
"entered when you created the category, and the Last check number. The Type "
"and Currency cannot be changed from their initial values."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek Splošno vam omogoča urejanje imena kategorije, morebitnih opomb, ki "
"ste jih vnesli, ko ste ustvarili kategorijo, in zadnje kontrolne številke. "
"Vrste in valute ni mogoče spremeniti iz njunih začetnih vrednosti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Hierarchy tab allows you to change the parent of the selected category "
"by clicking another category which then becomes the parent. In addition, you "
"can drag a category and drop it under its new parent."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek Hierarhija vam omogoča, da spremenite nadrejenega elementa izbrane "
"kategorije tako, da kliknete drugo kategorijo, ki nato postane nadrejena. "
"Poleg tega lahko povlečete kategorijo in jo spustite pod njen novi nadrejeni "
"element."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Tax tab allows you to assign or change VAT details, or to alter the "
"automatic VAT assignment. It also allows you to toggle whether or not the "
"category is included in tax related reports."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek Davek vam omogoča, da dodelite ali spremenite podrobnosti o DDV ali "
"spremenite samodejno dodelitev DDV. Omogoča tudi preklop, ali je kategorija "
"vključena v poročila, povezana z davki."

#. Tag: author
#: details-categories.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Thomas.Baumgart; &Thomas.Baumgart.mail;"
msgstr "&Thomas.Baumgart; &Thomas.Baumgart.mail;"

#. Tag: title
#: details-categories.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "VAT Support"
msgstr "DDV podpora"

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can turn an expense/income category into a VAT category, which means "
"that it receives all the splits that actually make up the VAT payment "
"towards the government. You can also enter a specific percentage rate."
msgstr ""
"Kategorijo odhodkov/prihodkov lahko spremenite v kategorijo DDV, kar pomeni, "
"da prejme vse delitve, ki dejansko sestavljajo plačilo DDV državi. Vnesete "
"lahko tudi določen odstotek."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Categories can be assigned a VAT category, which allows &kmymoney; to split "
"a transaction for a category into two parts, one for the category and one "
"for the VAT. Depending on the setting of the gross/net amount switch, the "
"amount you enter for the transaction is the gross or net amount."
msgstr ""
"Kategorijam je mogoče dodeliti kategorijo DDV, ki omogoča &kmymoney; da "
"transakcijo za kategorijo razdelite na dva dela, enega za kategorijo in "
"enega za DDV. Odvisno od nastavitve stikala bruto/neto znesek je znesek, ki "
"ga vnesete za transakcijo, bruto ali neto znesek."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Example: In Germany, there are three VAT percentages (0%, 7%, and 19%). So I "
"have a main category \"VAT paid\" and three subcategories, one for each "
"percentage rate. I create these on both the income and the expense sides so "
"that I have six categories in total. For the goods I buy, I select one of "
"the above mentioned categories as the \"VAT category assignment\"."
msgstr ""
"Primer: V Nemčiji obstajajo trije odstotki DDV (0%, 7% in 19%, v Sloveniji "
"0%, 5% in 21%). Tako imamo glavno kategorijo \"Plačan DDV\" in tri "
"podkategorije, eno za vsako odstotno stopnjo. Te ustvarimo tako na "
"prihodkovni kot na odhodkovni strani, tako da imamo skupaj šest kategorij. "
"Za blago, ki ga kupimo, izberem eno od zgoraj navedenih kategorij kot "
"»Dodelitev kategorije DDV«."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When I buy goods, I enter them into a transaction. Let's assume I have "
"selected the gross amount entry method, once I enter the category and "
"amount, &kmymoney; will recognize that there's a VAT assignment and "
"calculate the VAT part, create a second split with the VAT account and VAT "
"amount and reduce the category amount."
msgstr ""
"Ko kupimo blago, ga vnesemo v transakcijo. Recimo, da smo izbral način vnosa "
"bruto zneska, ko vnesemo kategorijo in znesek, &kmymoney; bo prepoznal, da "
"obstaja dodelitev DDV in izračunal del DDV, ustvaril drugo razdelitev z "
"računom DDV in zneskom DDV ter zmanjšal znesek kategorije."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In contrast, if you have selected the net amount entry method, the amount "
"you enter is treated as excluding VAT. &kmymoney; will calculate the VAT "
"portion, create a separate split for the VAT account, and leave the category "
"amount as entered."
msgstr ""
"V nasprotju, če ste izbrali metodo vnosa neto zneska, se vneseni znesek "
"obravnava kot znesek brez DDV. &kmymoney; bo izračunal del DDV, ustvaril "
"ločeno razdelitev za račun DDV in pustil znesek kategorije takšen, kot je "
"bil vnesen."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same applies to income categories but the other way around. Hope that "
"makes sense."
msgstr ""
"Enako velja za dohodkovne kategorije, vendar obratno. Upam, da je to "
"smiselno."

#. Tag: title
#: details-categories.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting a category"
msgstr "Brisanje kategorije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deleting a Category is similar to deleting an Account. To delete a category, "
"right-click its name in the Categories View, and select <guimenuitem>Delete "
"Category...</guimenuitem>. If the category has no transactions, schedules, "
"or budgets associated with it, and it is not set as the default category for "
"new transactions with any payee, it will be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Brisanje kategorije je podobno brisanju računa. Če želite izbrisati "
"kategorijo, z desno miškino tipko kliknite njeno ime v Pogledu kategorij in "
"izberite <guimenuitem>Izbriši kategorijo...</guimenuitem>. Če kategorija "
"nima povezanih transakcij, urnikov ali proračunov in ni nastavljena kot "
"privzeta kategorija za nove transakcije s katerim koli prejemnikom plačila, "
"bo izbrisana."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the category has any of those items, a popup will be displayed allowing "
"you to choose another category to which all those items can be reassigned "
"before the category is deleted."
msgstr ""
"Če ima kategorija katerega od teh elementov, se bo prikazalo pojavno okno, "
"ki vam bo omogočilo, da izberete drugo kategorijo, ki ji je mogoče vse te "
"elemente znova dodeliti, preden se kategorija izbriše."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you delete a category which is the parent of any other categories, a "
"dialog will be displayed for you to choose whether to delete that category "
"and all its sub-categories or just the parent category. If you choose to "
"just delete the parent category, then all its sub-categories will be moved "
"to its parent category."
msgstr ""
"Če izbrišete kategorijo, ki je nadrejena kateri koli drugi kategoriji, se "
"prikaže pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko izberete, ali želite izbrisati to "
"kategorijo in vse njene podkategorije ali samo nadrejeno kategorijo. Če se "
"odločite samo izbrisati nadrejeno kategorijo, bodo vse njene podkategorije "
"premaknjene v njeno nadrejeno kategorijo."

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that deleting some categories may prompt both for where to reassign its "
"data and also whether or not to delete any sub-categories."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da bo brisanje nekaterih kategorij morda zahtevalo, kam znova "
"dodeliti svoje podatke, in tudi, ali naj se izbrišejo podkategorije ali ne."

#. Tag: title
#: details-categories.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open ledger for a category"
msgstr "Odpri knjigo za kategorijo"

#. Tag: para
#: details-categories.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menu options for categories includes a choice to open a ledger for that "
"category. When this option is selected &kmymoney; will display that category "
"in a tab in the Ledgers View, showing all the transactions for the selected "
"category. This allows you to quickly review all the transactions in detail "
"for the selected category. You can then right-click any transaction to "
"obtain additional details about the specific transaction, and can even edit "
"the transaction."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti menija za kategorije vključujejo možnost odpiranja glavne knjige za "
"to kategorijo. Ko je izbrana ta možnost bo &kmymoney; to kategorijo prikazal "
"na zavihku v Pogledu knjig, kjer bodo prikazane vse transakcije za izbrano "
"kategorijo. Tako lahko hitro in podrobno pregledate vse transakcije za "
"izbrano kategorijo. Nato lahko z desno miškino tipko kliknete katero koli "
"transakcijo, da pridobite dodatne podrobnosti o določeni transakciji, in "
"lahko celo uredite transakcijo."

